name: compression_status
desc: A set of values used to represent the status of stream compression.

items.name: var COMPRESSION_STATUS_OK: compression_status
items.desc: Indicates the stream has consumed all data in the source buffer, or used all space in the destination buffer.

items.name: var COMPRESSION_STATUS_END: compression_status
items.desc: Indicates the stream has read all input from the source, and written all output to the destination.

items.name: var COMPRESSION_STATUS_ERROR: compression_status
items.desc: Indicates an error with stream compression.

items.desc: Creates a new constant from the given raw value.
